name: Nataicons
description:
A fun-themed simple open source icon by the folks at Natatoko. Practically, this icons are used on our web application, but feel free to use it on your project! 


This icons features:

  • Provide 2 icons variant: 24x24 and 20x20.
  • 238 icons and still growing (request if you need one).
  • Fully free and open-source.
  • Available as SVG sprites and Vue Components. Install it using npm.
